\[1^5+2^5+3^5+...+n^5 = \overset{n}{\underset{i=1}{\sum}} \,i^5 = \frac{n^2(n+1)^2(2n^2+2n-1)}{12}.\]

$PAR
Value of limit = \{ans_rule(30)\}

END_TEXT

